    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      Rofo helps businesses explore commercial real estate markets and connect with relevant opportunities.
      This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      When you use Rofo, we may collect basic information such as your name, email, phone number,
      and details about your space requirements when you submit a form.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>
      We use this information to respond to your inquiries, help match you with relevant
      commercial real estate opportunities, and improve the Rofo experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
    <p>
      In some cases, we may share your information with brokers, landlords, or service providers
      to help you find space. These parties may contact you directly regarding your request.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Rofo may link to or use third-party services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices
      of those services and encourage you to review their policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>
      We use reasonable security measures to protect your information. Access is limited to authorized individuals.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <p>
      You may request to update or delete your information at any time by contacting us.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@rofo.com">privacy@rofo.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
